{
  "texts": [
    "Finally, using feedback that are human interpretable and selectable opens new research avenues for personalized alignment of models.",
    "Users can potentially choose model-generated feedback that is most in line with their own preferences.",
    "Such feedback can then be used to ground the Edit model to make changes based on individual preferences in a controllable fashion.",
